  <brief_title>Skin-to-skin After Delivery in Preterm Infants Born at 28-32 Weeks of Gestation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Skin-to-skin After Delivery in Preterm Infants Born at 28-32 Weeks of Gestation. A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
